{"tid":1212314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[海外文宣] 海外撚想徵求大量黑警暴行嘅高清圖","createTime":"2019-06-12T18:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T03:03:15.000Z","uid":28053,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"65e73919562b623bc061e30347955c33851caffe","tid":1212314,"uid":28053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:06:30.000Z","msg":"海外嘅我地呢幾日睇到政府同警察嘅態度同暴行，大家都好嬲無又幫唔到咩手，失落感好重 返工都無心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地做到嘅就只有 接受訪問,翻譯,Post Reddit, 甚至寫左好多封唔同語言嘅信送出去...<br />\n<br />\n直到見到琴日警方嘅惡行，好多人都忍無可忍了<br />\n依家我地想問大家有無多D黑警惡行嘅圖/相，<br />\n例如以下呢種<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qyRjOU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qyRjOU.png&h=c2438dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者黑警開槍/催淚彈火花果啲，我地將會整大型poster貼街同印大量嘅傳單，希望令更多嘅人清楚同了解香港人依家嘅情況同所面對緊嘅後果，麻煩大家了 請俾我地盡一盡軟力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後香港嘅大家要小心，注意安全，呢場可能係一場持久戰 亦都係最後一戰。港人加油 天佑香港"},{"pid":"5de1b51620dcd33a52defaafac22d84590a2fdb3","tid":1212314,"uid":8922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382bf24353af3e7c35452d4eaeca71c8ebcf8201","tid":1212314,"uid":8922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f62ff57a19a6da06b33b6d171b172568b709b8","tid":1212314,"uid":100368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:32:11.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"bc4e09bbb9e534644a82f264ef90167479d3e3d7","tid":1212314,"uid":28053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"382bf24353af3e7c35452d4eaeca71c8ebcf8201","tid":1212314,"uid":8922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2